notes.about this file: This is essentially a formal restructuring of all details I've compiled for Omino, in preparation for an automated workflow that will convert this data into a proper normalized database.
misc: Examples can be examples of concepts (ex. grammar conditional tense) in addition to vocabulary.
Unnamed translations are under the "#noname" entry.
aliases are same-language mappings between synonyms. They should be restructured so there's no hierarchy, rather an unordered list of a-b pairs.
